<div class="section-{{ section.id }}-padding founders-{{ section.id }} color-{{ section.settings.color_scheme }}">
  <h2>Our Founders</h2>
  <p class="founders-intro">
    Young and agile graduates from IIT Guwahati wanted to use their technical skills in the food and agriculture industry.
    They have the vision to bring food processing to the farm level and provide traditional superfoods to everyone.
  </p>
    <div class="swiper mySwiper">
    <div class="swiper-wrapper">
      <div class="founder-card">
        <img src="kuldeep.jpg" alt="Kuldeep Parewa" class="founder-img" />
        <h3>Kuldeep Parewa</h3>
        <p>Being from a farming family, I know the hardships they face. Equipping them with technology, financial aid, and food-processing machines will generate more value for them. And in turn, this leads to healthy and traceable food for consumers.</p>
      </div>
  
      <div class="founder-card">
        <img src="aayushi.jpg" alt="Aayushi Khandelwal" class="founder-img" />
        <h3>Aayushi Khandelwal</h3>
        <p>I have always missed my nani's recipes and nuskhe in this modern lifestyle. I have the vision to preserve these with India's lost superfoods and connect modern consumers with traditional food.</p>
      </div>
  
      <div class="founder-card">
        <img src="akhil.jpg" alt="Akhil Kansal" class="founder-img" />
        <h3>Akhil Kansal</h3>
        <p>Using technology to assess food quality and create a direct-from-farm supply chain excites me the most. In this era of rising diseases, consumers need access to quality food, and farmers need to be empowered.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
      <!-- Arrows -->
    <div class="swiper-button-prev custom-nav">prev</div>
    <div class="swiper-button-next custom-nav">next</div>
    <div class="swiper-pagination"></div>
  </div>
</div>

<script>
  var swiper = new Swiper(".mySwiper", {
    slidesPerView: 1,
    spaceBetween: 30,
    loop: false,
    pagination: {
      el: ".swiper-pagination",
      clickable: true,
    },
    navigation: {
      nextEl: ".swiper-button-next",
      prevEl: ".swiper-button-prev",
    },
    breakpoints: {
      768: {
        slidesPerView: 1,
      },
      1024: {
        slidesPerView: 2,
      }
    }
  });
</script>
{% schema %}
  {
      "name": "Our Founder",
      "settings": [
        {
          "type": "color_scheme",
          "id": "color_scheme",
          "label": "t:sections.all.colors.label",
          "default": "background-1"
        },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "id": "title",
        "label": "Heading"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "id":"discription",
        "label":"Discription"
      },
      {
        "type": "range",
        "id": "padding_top",
        "min": 0,
        "max": 100,
        "step": 4,
        "unit": "px",
        "label": "t:sections.all.padding.padding_top",
        "default": 36
      },
      {
        "type": "range",
        "id": "padding_bottom",
        "min": 0,
        "max": 100,
        "step": 4,
        "unit": "px",
        "label": "t:sections.all.padding.padding_bottom",
        "default": 36
      }
      ],
      "blocks": [
        {
          "name": "Block",
          "type": "Block",
          "settings": [
            {
              "type": "image_picker",
              "id": "image",
              "label": "Founder Image"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id":"title",
              "label":"Customer Name"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id":"content",
              "label":"Discription"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "presets": [
        {
          "name": "Our Founder"
        }
      ]
    }
  {% endschema %}
<style>
    .section-{{ section.id }}-padding {
      padding-top: {{ section.settings.padding_top | times: 0.75 | round: 0 }}px;
      padding-bottom: {{ section.settings.padding_bottom | times: 0.75 | round: 0 }}px;
    }
    .founders-{{ section.id }} {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 60px 20px;
    }
    
    .founders-{{ section.id }} h2 {
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    
    .founders-{{ section.id }} .founders-intro {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto 50px;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #555;
    }
    
    .founders-{{ section.id }} .swiper-wrapper {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 30px;
      padding: 10px 20px;
    }
    
    .founders-{{ section.id }} .founder-card {
      background-color: white;
      border-radius: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      padding: 30px 20px;
      max-width: 320px;
      text-align: center;
      transition: transform 0.3s;
    }
    
    .founders-{{ section.id }} .founder-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
    }
    
    .founders-{{ section.id }} .founder-img {
      width: 120px;
      height: 120px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      object-fit: cover;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    
    .founders-{{ section.id }} .founder-card h3 {
      font-size: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    
    .founders-{{ section.id }} .founder-card p {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #444;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    @media screen and (min-width: 750px) {
    .section-{{ section.id }}-padding {
      padding-top: {{ section.settings.padding_top }}px;
      padding-bottom: {{ section.settings.padding_bottom }}px;
    }
</style>
